article.description: — Dawson Baker had a season-high 23 points as UC Irvine got past Cal State Fullerton 89-78 on Friday.
article.headline: Baker scores 23 to lift UC Irvine past CS Fullerton 89-78
article.linkText: Baker scores 23 to lift UC Irvine past CS Fullerton 89-78
article.story: FULLERTON, Calif. -- — Dawson Baker had a season-high 23 points as UC Irvine got past Cal State Fullerton 89-78 on Friday. Baker shot 10 for 12 from the line. JC Butler had 14 points for UC Irvine (12-7, 9-3 Big West Conference). Collin Welp added 13 points and 11 rebounds. DJ Davis had 11 points. Johnny Wang had 18 points for the Titans (5-7, 4-7). Dante Maddox Jr. added 14 points. Tray Maddox Jr. had 14 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
